{"tid":733402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人睇世界盃其實好難上心","createTime":"2018-07-07T17:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T15:40:50.000Z","uid":162112,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5162e9e95119ac6bb58e3457abdb224aebfa3679","tid":733402,"uid":162112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"成日好羨慕人地為自己國家隊流淚 激動<br />\n香港人 個個幫唔同國家<br />\n先唔講果班忽然港女淨係識一兩個足球明星 <br />\n又話心痛又話感動我dllm<br />\n<br />\n我識得真係成日睇足球又成日研究嘅<br />\n咪就係買左波 落左注果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫我贏錢 梗係鐘意佢地啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係土生土長當地人 鐘意嘅球隊贏波 興奮可能只係因為<br />\n你買左果隊贏<br />\n世界盃帶黎嘅氣氛<br />\n自滿自己嘅眼光<br />\n<br />\n但係世界盃(唔計英超果啲唔係國家做單位)<br />\n人地興奮 係因為歸屬感<br />\n<br />\n我羨慕人地對球隊嘅歸屬感下睇球果種肉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259cfcdccad169f81ad4573ae22f37d733890a5e","tid":733402,"uid":162112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d93de3df737315aeddae3b25574a06a1f21e731","tid":733402,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"黎緊亞運有機會"},{"pid":"c90194f32b5b9e0c35b220033c3bc582a91003b4","tid":733402,"uid":162112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d93de3df737315aeddae3b25574a06a1f21e731","tid":733402,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"黎緊亞運有機會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629abbefbda3a09a13a8c0306fa81ee343da0de3","tid":733402,"uid":162112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class